# Import map policy
- All deps are mapped in `public/index.html` using `<script type="importmap">`.
- Use **pinned versions** from `https://esm.sh/` and prefer stable targets.
- Example baseline (adjust versions as needed):

```html
<!-- public/index.html -->
<script type="importmap">
{
  "imports": {
    "react": "https://esm.sh/react@18.3.1",
    "react-dom": "https://esm.sh/react-dom@18.3.1",
    "zustand": "https://esm.sh/zustand@4.5.2",
    "zod": "https://esm.sh/zod@3.23.8"
  }
}
</script>
